{"tid":1770993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個分化撚開po屌教畜唔罷工，竟然有好多人like","createTime":"2019-12-05T13:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T17:01:05.000Z","uid":113155,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"75af2ae8451344c8322784b8051dee85373ea83d","tid":1770993,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGenaNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGenaNx.png&h=33e9f46b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個百幾個係咪唔識起底？<br />\n條友罷明分化撚黎。<br />\n<br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人<br />\n首先大家有眼見，香港人只可以被罷工，係冇咩可能搞到全民長期罷工，你自己做唔到，請唔好逼人。<br />\n<br />\n其次，教畜業十間學校九間紅，剩底一間係藍。<br />\n而教畜業競爭非常激烈，僧多粥少，你叫晒啲黃老師罷工，得，直炒，請番晒啲藍老師。<br />\n到時係喊都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n班學生咁黃，你諗下點解啦屌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請善用起底功能</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce61f2c55829de3fa50a1ab9edf4f12c74ccf9d4","tid":1770993,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"心清啲啦大家，唔好得一腔熱血"},{"pid":"08d65d9e58c0f03ec4e4273854f67c47695d2ba0","tid":1770993,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"分化撚可齒"},{"pid":"aff88f3ac46987682f594eb5bff8a7e1f869c265","tid":1770993,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"幫手推，仲有好撚多人like佢，係咪痴線"},{"pid":"ed48ffc008ecfbb94875db91425dfcea78659248","tid":1770993,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"條友睇真啲，條友仲係標題黨"},{"pid":"8e0affa8fc773415a0ae886b4afc25594ddc31d5","tid":1770993,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:43:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a64a6673df6edef454a2659f38d2d1a323d4fc3d","tid":1770993,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"希望係01嗰五百個打手like la"},{"pid":"ad9546fcb71fa40c21e3048dcf